{"cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "status": "RESOLVED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox61": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox62": "---", "creator": "moz-ian@perix.co.uk", "mentors_detail": [], "depends_on": [], "cf_status_firefox_esr60": "---", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "All", "cf_status_firefox58": "unaffected", "cf_status_firefox59": "disabled", "keywords": ["regression"], "cf_status_firefox57": "unaffected", "summary": "The taller a table caption is the more rows of a table lose their border with border-collapse: collapse", "cf_last_resolved": "2018-04-26T14:17:04Z", "attachments": [{"creator": "moz-ian@perix.co.uk", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "text/html", "id": 8943001}, {"creator": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2018-04-25T19:27:56Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2018-04-23T19:18:18Z", "id": 1747865, "setter": "mstange@themasta.com"}], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8970306}, {"creator": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [{"status": "+", "name": "review", "modification_date": "2018-04-25T19:29:23Z", "type_id": 4, "creation_date": "2018-04-25T19:21:23Z", "id": 1749033, "setter": "mstange@themasta.com"}], "content_type": "text/x-review-board-request", "id": 8970937}], "votes": 1, "classification": "Components", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "yes", "comment_count": 16, "comments": [{"text": "Created attachment 8943001\nTestcase\n\nSTR:\n1) set gfx.webrender.all to true in about:config and restart\n2) load the attached testcase\n3) observe unrendered borders\n\nThe number of rows without borders seems to be almost Math.floor(captionHeight / rowHeight), so there's a nice N-1 rows deleted to N rows of caption relation in the testcase.", "author": "moz-ian@perix.co.uk", "id": 12972874, "time": "2018-01-16T19:45:51Z"}, {"text": "mozregression --good 2017-05-01 --bad 2017-10-01 --pref layers.acceleration.force-enabled:true gfx.webrender.enabled:true gfx.webrendest.enabled:true gfx.webrender.blob-images:true gfx.webrender.layers-free:true startup.homepage_welcome_url:\"https://bug1430869.bmoattachments.org/attachment.cgi?id=8943001\"\n> 5:56.04 INFO: Last good revision: 5a8f2dcbeac0677b5aae0f9fd43d6a33309b4a6b\n> 5:56.04 INFO: First bad revision: 979f11deabd01d6cb897d064d3d9ed11ea8baa93\n> 5:56.04 INFO: Pushlog:\n> https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/pushloghtml?fromchange=5a8f2dcbeac0677b5aae0f9fd43d6a33309b4a6b&tochange=979f11deabd01d6cb897d064d3d9ed11ea8baa93\n> \n> 5:57.23 ERROR: Unable to exploit the merge commit. Origin branch is mozilla-central, and the commit message for 979f11de was:\n> Merge graphics to m-c a=merge a=release\n> IGNORE BAD COMMIT MESSAGES because something landed and was backed out for no bug number", "author": "jan@ikenmeyer.eu", "id": 12973064, "time": "2018-01-16T21:03:52Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to Jan Andre Ikenmeyer [:darkspirit] from comment #1)\n> > 5:56.04 INFO: Pushlog:\n> > https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/pushloghtml?fromchange=5a8f2dcbeac0677b5aae0f9fd43d6a33309b4a6b&tochange=979f11deabd01d6cb897d064d3d9ed11ea8baa93\n> > \n\nProbably from the original table implementation in bug 1344082.", "author": "bugmail@mozilla.staktrace.com", "id": 12973179, "time": "2018-01-16T21:29:36Z"}, {"text": "Not an accessibility issue, but looks like a graphics bug to me. Clearing a11y review flag.", "author": "mzehe@mozilla.com", "id": 13107544, "time": "2018-03-06T10:34:18Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8970306\nBug 1430869 - use mVisibleRect instead of GetRect.\n\nAn ancient comment from 1998 assures us that GetRect is wrong if there are captions.\nThe painting code instead uses mVisibleRect which appears to be correct.\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/239098/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/239098/", "author": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "id": 13227470, "time": "2018-04-23T19:18:18Z"}, {"text": "try: https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=4f7f0d7685fd697f084783aa13f2fef8ae17c065", "author": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "id": 13227480, "time": "2018-04-23T19:21:50Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8970306\nBug 1430869 - use mVisibleRect instead of GetRect.\n\nMarkus is a better reviewer than me.", "author": "jmuizelaar@mozilla.com", "id": 13227483, "time": "2018-04-23T19:24:11Z"}, {"text": "Try looks good, but suggests I need to write a regression test.", "author": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "id": 13227765, "time": "2018-04-23T20:57:53Z"}, {"text": "Try with test: https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=82679e9a8221fc98007c9d96f1c34f3731334e32", "author": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "id": 13232971, "time": "2018-04-25T16:27:51Z"}, {"text": "Created attachment 8970937\nBug 1430869 - add reftest for border collapse and captions.\n\nReview commit: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/239696/diff/#index_header\nSee other reviews: https://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/239696/", "author": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "id": 13232979, "time": "2018-04-25T16:30:38Z"}, {"text": "Try looks good, ready for review.", "author": "a.beingessner@gmail.com", "id": 13232986, "time": "2018-04-25T16:33:04Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8970306\nBug 1430869 - use mVisibleRect instead of GetRect.\n\nhttps://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/239098/#review245426", "author": "mstange@themasta.com", "id": 13233486, "time": "2018-04-25T19:27:56Z"}, {"text": "Comment on attachment 8970937\nBug 1430869 - add reftest for border collapse and captions.\n\nhttps://reviewboard.mozilla.org/r/239696/#review245430", "author": "mstange@themasta.com", "id": 13233492, "time": "2018-04-25T19:29:23Z"}, {"text": "Pushed by ryanvm@gmail.com:\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/integration/autoland/rev/04465c06888b\nuse mVisibleRect instead of GetRect. r=mstange\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/integration/autoland/rev/9536d401ce06\nadd reftest for border collapse and captions. r=mstange", "author": "pulsebot@bots.tld", "id": 13234680, "time": "2018-04-26T08:05:26Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/04465c06888b\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/9536d401ce06", "author": "apavel@mozilla.com", "id": 13235324, "time": "2018-04-26T14:17:04Z"}, {"text": "I could reproduce this bug only on Windows 10 x32 platform with the Nightly build 59.0a1 (2018-01-16). On Nightly 62.0a1 (2018-05-21) and Beta 61.0b6 the issue is no longer reproducible. \nI couldn\u2019t see the issue, neither on Windows 10 x64, on Beta 61.0b (on the latest Nightly I encountered the same behavior mentioned in bug 1461647, so I was unable to verified it), nor on macOS 10.13 on the same latest Firefox builds (61.0b6 and 62.0a1).\n\nOn Ubuntu 16.04 x32, the issue is still reproducible on the latest Firefox version(see screenshot: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1G5GJQN-qFeEb1E0cyjuHIsnPGHm_-ntg). \n\nI would also add that, the related issue mentioned above (bug 1461054) is reproducible, both on Ubuntu 16.04 x32 and macOS 10.13, but not on Windows platforms.", "author": "anca.soncutean@softvision.ro", "id": 13294352, "time": "2018-05-21T15:47:54Z"}], "id": 1430869, "priority": "P1", "cc": ["anca.soncutean@softvision.ro", "bogdan.maris@softvision.ro", "bugmail@mozilla.staktrace.com", "jan@ikenmeyer.eu", "jmuizelaar@mozilla.com", "milaninbugzilla@gmail.com", "mstange@themasta.com", "sledru@mozilla.com"], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "Trunk", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "see_also": ["https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1461054"], "cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr60": "---", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "blocks": [1386669, 1423269, 1344082], "qa_contact": "", "creation_time": "2018-01-16T19:45:51Z", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "unaffect